    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2005-07-28</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2005-08-18T20:13:46Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Badge and Uniform Security and Trustworthiness Act of 2005 - Amends the federal criminal code to apply prohibitions against the use of counterfeit police badges to the use of any official insignia or article of clothing (including a badge, emblem or identification card, that is an indicium of the authority of a public employee). Defines &quot;public employee&quot; to mean any officer or employee of the federal government or of a state or local government. </p> <p>Directs the U.S. Sentencing Commission to amend the sentencing guidelines to assure that the sentence imposed on a defendant who is convicted of a federal offense while wearing or displaying such insignia and clothing reflects the gravity of this aggravating factor.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
